title: Women in Film
description:
A panel from the best in the industry, about women in film.

Written by Katelyn Trela

Featuring  Maya Deshmukh, Tessa Hersh, Tristan Griffin, Chrissy Shackelford and Michael Delisle
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
